These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-7-1::.
City: paris, miami, berlin
1. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to paris##5
2. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere between the person traveling to paris and the person traveling to miami##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |  3   |
| City   | paris | berlin | miami |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-7-2::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, badminton, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's sport is biathlon##7
2. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |
| Sport   | biathlon | ice-hockey | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-7-3::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, red, black
1. the person who likes coral is somewhere between the person who likes red and the person who likes black##7
2. the person who likes red is somewhere to the left of the person who likes coral##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |   3    |
| Color   | red | coral | black |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-7-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, mexican, polish
1. the mexican is somewhere between the polish and the dutch##7
2. the polish is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |
| Nationality   | dutch | mexican | polish |

