2. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the left of the person eating cauliflower##5
3. the person eating carrot is somewhere between the person eating cauliflower and the person eating lemon##7

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2    |       3       |
| Food   | lemon | carrot | cauliflower |

